Detailed Description

Advanced DLB event send structure. For use with dlb_adv_send().

Member Data Documentation

◆ @21

union { ... }

For the BAT_T command, the field indicates the number of tokens to return. For NEW/NEW_T and FWD/FWD_T commands, the flow_id field specifies the event's flow ID.
